# Add, edit, and delete a software

## Add a software

1. In the left-hand navigation bar, select the **Software** tab.
2. Click the **Add** button.
3. Fill in the required software details.
4. Click **Publish** to save and add the software.

## Edit a software

1. In the left-hand navigation bar, go to the **Software** tab.
2. Double-click on the row of the software you want to edit.
3. Make the necessary changes to the software details.
4. Click **Publish** to save your changes.

## Delete a software

1. In the left-hand navigation bar, select the **Software** tab.
2. Double-click on the row of the software you want to delete.
3. Click the **Delete** button in the top-right corner of the screen.
4. In the confirmation popup, click **Confirm** to finalize the deletion.